HEADWORD: Bennet
<hw>Ben"net</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>beno⟦icir⟧te</ets>, fr. L. <ets>benedicta</ets>, fem. of
